title: r/Choosingbeggars Seeking Free House - NEW HOUSES ONLY!
description: r/Choosingbeggars Does anybody know of any free houses that I could have? I know that everyone needs a place to live but, frankly, I'm more important than you and I deserve a free house. Oh, and I only want a NEW house! Not some old, run-down house. What do I look like, a poor person? Ha! As if! If you like this video, follow my podcast for more daily Reddit content!
